  "title": "Hair Stylist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Basic knowledge and skills in hair cutting, Washing, Blow out, Treatment and Colouring.</li>\n  <li>Advising clients on styles, colours and treatment best suited for them.</li>\n  <li>Applying hair care products such as treatment oils and masks.</li>\n  <li>Salon housekeeping and Other Adhoc duties</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preferably with Nitec/Certification specialized in Hair and Beauty</li>\n  <li>Work experience as a Hair Stylist, Hairdresser, Colourist or similar role are preferred. </li>\n  <li>Entry level candidates are also welcome to apply.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in hair straightening and curling methods, using hot irons and curlers</li>\n  <li>Hands-on experience with various colouring techniques</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of a wide range of haircuts, suitable for all hair lengths</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with hair treatment products and services, like keratin treatment</li>\n  <li>Up-to-date with industry trends</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills</li>\n</ul>",
